<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.6">
<l>eṅṅaṉum nāmivar vaṇṇameṇṇi lētuma ṟikila mēntiḻaiyār</l>
<l>caṅkumma ṉamuni ṟaivumellām tammaṉa vāka<supplied>p</supplied>pu  kuntutāmum</l>
<l>poṅkuka ruṅkaṭal pūvaikāyāp pōtaviḻ nīlampu ṉaintamēkam</l>
<l>aṅṅaṉam pōṉṟiva rārkkoleṉṉa</l>
<l>vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If we somehow consider his nature,</l>
<l rend="indent">we are [still] not be able to know anything!</l>
<l>When I asked, “Who is this appearing the same as the dark roiling sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">pūvai and kāyā buds, furled dark lilies, and ornate clouds,</l>
<l>Arriving so that bejeweled ladies themselves, and all of their bangles,</l>
<l rend="indent">hearts, and perfection, become [his] own?”</l>
<l>He answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
